<section class="el-home__section">
  <h2 class="el-home__section-title">From L2 documented to L4 AI-native — without the hype loop.</h2>
  <p class="el-home__lede">
    Every Sunday, one diagnostic prompt and one Monday move &mdash; designed for leaders
