    team operations.
  </p>
  <p class="el-home__lede">
    <strong>Where does your team sit on the L1&ndash;L5 ladder?</strong> If you cannot
    answer that in one sentence, the first edition is built for you. If you can, the
    Monday move is built for the next rung.
  </p>
  <div class="el-hero__cta-slot">
    {{ bvp_signup_cta('inline', 'Subscribe to Elevationary', '/subscribe/') }}
  </div>
</section>

